Timelaps 1600

   webcam Puy-Saint-Vincent

   With more than 50% of its ski area above 2000m, Puy Saint Vincent
   offers, thanks to an abundant snow, a good skiing during whole winter.

   Puy Saint Vincent is: 1550m of vertical descent, four fun areas, one
   boardercross, one slope for night skiing, artificial snow cover from
   1400m to 2100m, 35 km of cross country skiing, 90 ha ski area….

   View our special offers

